                            <comment id="17476291" author="davsclaus" created="Fri, 14 Jan 2022 17:27:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Its *** spring that creates this class too soon, as camel context is not created first - the class is @component so spring decides the order they are created&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
